= render "layouts/simple-header"

.main-visual
  .main-visual__box
    .main-visual__box__contents
      %h2.main-visual__box__contents__subtitle  人生を変えるフリマアプリ
      %p.main-visual__box__contents__text  
        FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる
        %br
        フリマアプリです
      .main-visual__box__contents__btn
        = link_to "#", class: "main-visual__box__contents__btn__a-link" do
          = image_tag src="https://web-jp-assets.mercdn.net/_next/static/images/app-store-a5c17948c6fd6d5b60b13d421cd60b35.svg", class: "main-visual__box__contents__btn__a-link__app"
        = link_to "#", class: "main-visual__box__contents__btn__g-link" do
          = image_tag src="https://web-jp-assets.mercdn.net/_next/static/images/google-play-495575abb895b405aa6336b2a4304958.svg", class: "main-visual__box__contents__btn__g-link__google"

.top-introduction
  %h2.top-introduction__subtitle  FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
  %ul.top-introduction__lists
    %li.top-introduction__lists__list
      .top-introduction__lists__list__pict
        %span.top-introduction__lists__list__pict__number  1
        = image_tag 'pict/pict-reason-01.jpg', class: 'top-introduction__lists__list__pict__image'
      %h3.top-introduction__lists__list__text  
        %span 3分
        ですぐに出品
      %p.top-introduction__lists__list__description  スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！

    %li.top-introduction__lists__list
      .top-introduction__lists__list__pict
        %span.top-introduction__lists__list__pict__number  2
        = image_tag 'pict/pict-reason-02.jpg', class: 'top-introduction__lists__list__pict__image'
      %h3.top-introduction__lists__list__text  
        %span  シンプル  
        で使いやすい
      %p.top-introduction__lists__list__description  めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！

    %li.top-introduction__lists__list__last.top-introduction__lists__list
      .top-introduction__lists__list__pict
        %span.top-introduction__lists__list__pict__number  3
        = image_tag 'pict/pict-reason-03.jpg', class: 'top-introduction__lists__list__pict__image'
      %h3.top-introduction__lists__list__text 
        手数料  
        %span  業界最安
      %p.top-introduction__lists__list__description  最大3%でお得に出品&購入！

.top-middledl
  .top-middledl__inner
    %h2.top-middledl__inner__subtitle 会員数日本一位
    %p.top-middledl__inner__text 
      FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
      %br
      出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
      %br
      ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
    .top-middledl__inner__btn
      = link_to "#", class: "top-middledl__inner__btn__a-link" do
        = image_tag src="https://web-jp-assets.mercdn.net/_next/static/images/app-store-a5c17948c6fd6d5b60b13d421cd60b35.svg", class: "top-middledl__inner__btn__a-link__app"
      = link_to "#", class: "top-middledl__inner__btn__g-link" do
        = image_tag src="https://web-jp-assets.mercdn.net/_next/static/images/google-play-495575abb895b405aa6336b2a4304958.svg", class: "top-middledl__inner__btn__g-link__google"

.topkey-feater
  %h2.topkey-feater__head  FURIMAの特徴
  .topkey-feater__items
    .topkey-feater__items__item
      %figure.topkey-feater__items__item__img
        = image_tag "icon/icon-01.png", class: "topkey-feater__items__item__img__icon"
      %h3.topkey-feater__items__item__subtitle  簡単に売り買いできる
      %p.topkey-feater__items__item__detail  スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
    .topkey-feater__items__item
      %figure.topkey-feater__items__item__img
        = image_tag "icon/icon-03.png", class: "topkey-feater__items__item__img__icon"
      %h3.topkey-feater__items__item__subtitle  売上金は即日振込みに対応
      %p.topkey-feater__items__item__detail  午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
    .topkey-feater__items__item
      %figure.topkey-feater__items__item__img
        = image_tag "icon/icon-04.png", class: "topkey-feater__items__item__img__icon"
      %h3.topkey-feater__items__item__subtitle  様々な支払いに対応
      %p.topkey-feater__items__item__detail  お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。

